WEBVTT

STYLE
::cue(c.color9CD5FF) { color: #9CD5FF; }
::cue(c.colora8c7fa) { color: #a8c7fa; }

1
00:00:01.000 --> 00:00:04.000 line:0
<b><c.color9CD5FF>One Pace Premium</c></b>
Keep the project alive: <c.colora8c7fa>ko-fi.com/not6ip</c>

2
00:00:06.900 --> 00:00:10.510
What's with you?! Stop this nonsense!

3
00:00:11.690 --> 00:00:14.600
Why do you need to fight?
You two are friends!

4
00:00:14.600 --> 00:00:18.160
Give it some time, and the two
of you will cool off, right?

5
00:00:18.570 --> 00:00:22.120
And Usopp! He just got fired up
because of how unexpected all this was.

6
00:00:23.010 --> 00:00:25.380
It's too late to back out now.

7
00:00:26.300 --> 00:00:27.570
That's not true!

8
00:00:27.570 --> 00:00:31.090
You can apologize and talk it over with him!

9
00:00:32.900 --> 00:00:36.970
Like I said... it's too late.

10
00:00:36.970 --> 00:00:38.720
What do you mean?

11
00:00:38.720 --> 00:00:44.250
Usopp isn't stupid enough to risk
his life over a temper tantrum.

12
00:00:44.250 --> 00:00:49.940
Besides, if talking is all it takes to change
his mind, it wouldn't have gone this far.

13
00:00:51.090 --> 00:00:52.940
If you get it, leave me alone.

14
00:00:54.440 --> 00:00:55.600
Luffy...

15
00:00:55.600 --> 00:01:00.660
That's just it! The Franky Family
came by this afternoon, right?!

16
00:01:00.660 --> 00:01:03.240
Huh? What are you getting at?!

17
00:01:03.240 --> 00:01:07.330
Why didn't you take the opportunity
to beat them to a pulp then?!

18
00:01:07.330 --> 00:01:11.900
If you had, they wouldn't have attacked Usopp,
who now feels responsible for all this!

19
00:01:11.900 --> 00:01:16.840
Okay, then instead of going shopping,
you should've stayed and kicked their teeth in!

20
00:01:16.840 --> 00:01:19.250
It's the cook's job to procure essentials!

21
00:01:19.250 --> 00:01:21.810
This is no time to be fighting!

22
00:01:21.810 --> 00:01:24.140
There's already been plenty of that.

23
00:01:25.690 --> 00:01:28.000
Don't argue over what can't be undone.

24
00:01:28.000 --> 00:01:31.610
Nami...! But this idiot is...

25
00:01:35.090 --> 00:01:39.070
Chopper, weren't you... following Usopp?

26
00:01:42.000 --> 00:01:46.830
I wanted to keep treating his wounds,
but he turned me away.

27
00:01:47.740 --> 00:01:51.070
He got a place to stay in town.

28
00:01:51.950 --> 00:01:53.760
He said...

29
00:01:54.330 --> 00:01:59.760
He said, "You and I are no longer
crewmates, so go back to the ship!"

30
00:02:04.210 --> 00:02:07.640
It's like all the great times we had
before today were an illusion.

31
00:02:11.100 --> 00:02:15.070
To top it all off, something
may have happened to Robin.

32
00:02:15.550 --> 00:02:18.030
I feel like... our crew...

33
00:02:18.700 --> 00:02:20.690
is falling apart.

34
00:02:27.110 --> 00:02:29.300
It's ten o'clock, the promised time.

35
00:02:29.300 --> 00:02:31.080
Usopp will be here.

36
00:02:40.650 --> 00:02:43.760
You guys! Stay on board
and don't come down here!

37
00:02:43.760 --> 00:02:45.030
Got that?!

38
00:02:51.830 --> 00:02:52.570
There he is!

39
00:02:52.570 --> 00:02:54.030
Usopp!

40
00:03:17.700 --> 00:03:20.020
So you didn't back down, huh?

41
00:03:20.020 --> 00:03:22.930
Just don't regret this later,
no matter how it ends!

42
00:03:22.930 --> 00:03:25.390
You asked for this duel!

43
00:03:25.390 --> 00:03:28.640
Of course. Bring it on.

44
00:03:28.640 --> 00:03:30.730
I'll turn the tables on you.

45
00:03:30.730 --> 00:03:34.360
I've already figured out how to defeat you.

46
00:03:34.870 --> 00:03:38.360
Can't we stop them?
Usopp is seriously injured!

47
00:03:38.360 --> 00:03:40.450
Go inside if you can't watch.

48
00:03:41.210 --> 00:03:44.900
I'm not like your past enemies
who weren't familiar with your abilities.

49
00:03:44.900 --> 00:03:48.850
Luffy, we've known each other a long time.

50
00:03:49.400 --> 00:03:52.420
I know your powers very well.

51
00:05:45.130 --> 00:05:47.490
What I say might surprise you, Luffy...

52
00:05:47.490 --> 00:05:50.370
I have 8,000 men under me!

53
00:05:51.090 --> 00:05:54.790
If you value your life, surrender now!

54
00:05:55.120 --> 00:05:57.910
What?! Eight thousand?! That many?!

55
00:05:57.910 --> 00:05:59.540
Just go inside.

56
00:05:59.540 --> 00:06:02.590
I already know you don't have any men!

57
00:06:02.590 --> 00:06:05.130
Usopp Spell!

58
00:06:05.130 --> 00:06:08.720
You've got razor blades
running between your teeth!

59
00:06:09.690 --> 00:06:12.000
It hurts just to imagine that!

60
00:06:12.000 --> 00:06:13.510
Go inside.

61
00:06:13.510 --> 00:06:16.640
You've got cactus spines
stuck under your nails!

62
00:06:18.060 --> 00:06:19.520
Gum-Gum...

63
00:06:19.520 --> 00:06:21.520
Pistol!

64
00:06:26.900 --> 00:06:28.240
Usopp!

65
00:06:29.690 --> 00:06:32.200
See?! He's in bad shape!

66
00:06:33.850 --> 00:06:36.660
Lethal... Ketchup Star!

67
00:06:37.200 --> 00:06:41.750
What's that? Feeling sorry
for your enemy? How arrogant!

68
00:06:41.750 --> 00:06:43.090
Flash Dial!

69
00:06:48.650 --> 00:06:50.720
Lethal Egg Star!

70
00:06:52.890 --> 00:06:53.560
Star!

71
00:06:53.560 --> 00:06:54.270
Star!

72
00:06:54.270 --> 00:06:55.140
Star!

73
00:06:57.980 --> 00:06:59.690
It stinks! They're rotten!

74
00:07:00.050 --> 00:07:03.100
Dammit, you jerk! Take this seriously!

75
00:07:03.100 --> 00:07:06.030
Think I'm fooling around?! I am serious, Luffy!

76
00:07:06.030 --> 00:07:07.030
What?

77
00:07:07.030 --> 00:07:09.240
This... is how I fight!

78
00:07:09.690 --> 00:07:12.240
Take care your gaping mouth
doesn't get burned!

79
00:07:16.330 --> 00:07:18.750
Lethal Tabasco Star!

80
00:07:18.750 --> 00:07:21.710
It burns!

81
00:07:22.020 --> 00:07:24.670
Watch how you thrash about!

82
00:07:24.670 --> 00:07:28.010
Or your feet will know my Caltrop Hell!

83
00:07:29.840 --> 00:07:31.300
Ouch!

84
00:07:32.220 --> 00:07:33.760
Usopp's controlling the fight!

85
00:07:34.640 --> 00:07:36.600
Listen, Luffy!

86
00:07:34.760 --> 00:07:40.020
Luffy vs. Usopp

87
00:07:36.600 --> 00:07:40.020
Rest assured, I'll beat you and take the Merry,

88
00:07:40.020 --> 00:07:42.020
no matter what it takes!

89
00:07:43.270 --> 00:07:45.020
Lethal Pepper Star!

90
00:07:47.190 --> 00:07:48.990
Ouch!

91
00:07:56.270 --> 00:07:59.660
Didn't I warn you? I'm only using
attacks that work against you!

92
00:08:03.690 --> 00:08:08.840
Dammit. It stinks... my mouth is burning...

93
00:08:08.840 --> 00:08:10.340
and it hurts!

94
00:08:10.730 --> 00:08:12.500
You won't get a chance to hit back!

95
00:08:12.500 --> 00:08:14.790
Lethal Shuriken Meteor Shower!

96
00:08:58.680 --> 00:08:59.600
Smoke?

97
00:09:02.700 --> 00:09:04.380
I'm using a breath dial.

98
00:09:06.410 --> 00:09:09.520
I take it the smell was masked by the eggs.

99
00:09:13.780 --> 00:09:16.740
The smell of the gas filling the air around you!

100
00:09:17.460 --> 00:09:18.410
Gas?

101
00:09:18.410 --> 00:09:19.780
He didn't...!

102
00:09:20.500 --> 00:09:22.040
Sorry! Take this!

103
00:09:22.600 --> 00:09:24.250
Fire Star!

104
00:09:37.010 --> 00:09:38.800
That's some explosion!

105
00:09:45.850 --> 00:09:47.690
Luffy! Usopp!

106
00:09:58.710 --> 00:10:03.410
I am Usopp, leader of the great pirates
who reign over this village!

107
00:10:03.410 --> 00:10:09.790
People praise me—and then they praise me
more—and refer to me as Captain Usopp!

108
00:10:18.760 --> 00:10:20.340
You're hilarious!

109
00:10:20.880 --> 00:10:23.340
Hey, you! Don't insult me!

110
00:10:23.340 --> 00:10:24.560
How come?

111
00:10:24.560 --> 00:10:27.270
You're one of us now, aren't you?

112
00:10:31.110 --> 00:10:33.740
I see an island!

113
00:10:33.740 --> 00:10:37.070
Whoa! Incredible! What kind of island is that?!

114
00:10:37.070 --> 00:10:39.410
All right! Go!

115
00:10:39.410 --> 00:10:42.500
Merry, full speed ahead!

116
00:10:42.500 --> 00:10:44.950
Full speed ahead!

117
00:11:15.270 --> 00:11:17.030
This is too much.

118
00:11:17.030 --> 00:11:20.130
Luffy! Usopp!

119
00:11:37.100 --> 00:11:41.760
I figured... an attack like that
wouldn't take you out.

120
00:11:41.760 --> 00:11:43.590
I know you, Luffy.

121
00:11:44.300 --> 00:11:47.700
You push your limits in every battle.

122
00:11:49.420 --> 00:11:52.070
I know your abilities all too well!

123
00:11:56.440 --> 00:11:57.730
Lethal...

124
00:11:57.730 --> 00:11:59.150
Gum-Gum...

125
00:11:59.150 --> 00:12:01.490
Gatling!

126
00:12:01.490 --> 00:12:03.700
...Bursting Cactus Star!

127
00:12:10.410 --> 00:12:12.120
Ouch!

128
00:12:14.300 --> 00:12:16.090
Triple Exploding Stars!

129
00:12:30.560 --> 00:12:32.430
Gum-Gum...

130
00:12:32.430 --> 00:12:33.690
Pistol!

131
00:12:45.990 --> 00:12:48.330
Gum-Gum...

132
00:12:48.330 --> 00:12:51.080
Bazooka!

133
00:12:56.210 --> 00:12:58.500
With this dial...

134
00:12:58.500 --> 00:13:02.090
I absorbed the impact of your attack!

135
00:13:03.760 --> 00:13:05.090
Impact!

136
00:13:10.680 --> 00:13:12.350
An impact dial!

137
00:13:20.070 --> 00:13:22.990
How'd you like that?! Dammit!

138
00:13:51.790 --> 00:13:58.060
I am Usopp, leader of the great pirates
who reign over this village!

139
00:14:03.290 --> 00:14:05.650
To our new ship and crewmate!

140
00:14:05.650 --> 00:14:08.660
– Cheers!
– Cheers!

141
00:14:11.010 --> 00:14:12.100
Something like this?

142
00:14:12.100 --> 00:14:14.330
It looks good! Let's draw it on the sail too!

143
00:14:14.740 --> 00:14:16.210
Alright! All done!

144
00:14:16.210 --> 00:14:20.540
Our pirate ship,
the Going Merry, is finally ready!

145
00:14:21.700 --> 00:14:25.550
Gum-Gum...

146
00:14:25.550 --> 00:14:27.730
Bullet!

147
00:14:37.700 --> 00:14:39.770
Usopp!

148
00:15:07.600 --> 00:15:09.130
Fight's over.

149
00:15:23.610 --> 00:15:25.180
You idiot...!

150
00:15:27.400 --> 00:15:32.210
There's no possible way...
you could've defeated me!

151
00:15:58.860 --> 00:16:01.210
No... no more...

152
00:16:10.810 --> 00:16:13.780
Do what you want with the Merry.

153
00:16:17.300 --> 00:16:22.930
As for us, we'll get a new ship
and keep sailing forward!

154
00:16:24.210 --> 00:16:26.200
Hey! Let me sit there too, Luffy!

155
00:16:26.200 --> 00:16:29.170
No! This is my special seat!

156
00:16:29.170 --> 00:16:31.100
Oh? What's that?!

157
00:16:31.100 --> 00:16:32.670
What're you making, Usopp?

158
00:16:32.670 --> 00:16:37.090
Whoa! You guys! Don't just
tromp around Usopp's Factory!

159
00:16:46.800 --> 00:16:50.360
Someday, I will go to Elbaf!

160
00:16:50.360 --> 00:16:52.990
To the village of warriors!

161
00:16:52.990 --> 00:16:56.990
All right, Usopp!
Let's make sure we go there!

162
00:16:57.420 --> 00:17:02.470
Let's get this party started!
It's the gold-hunting eve festival!

163
00:17:12.410 --> 00:17:14.300
So long, Usopp.

164
00:17:15.160 --> 00:17:18.040
It's been fun.

165
00:17:22.850 --> 00:17:24.770
Hey, don't go, Chopper!

166
00:17:26.060 --> 00:17:27.360
Why shouldn't I?!

167
00:17:27.360 --> 00:17:31.480
His injuries were already pretty serious,
and now he's in even worse shape!

168
00:17:32.660 --> 00:17:34.410
This wasn't just a quarrel or a game.

169
00:17:34.410 --> 00:17:39.030
What's your point?! I'm a doctor!
Let me at least treat him!

170
00:17:43.660 --> 00:17:47.390
He lost the duel.
The last thing he wants is our pity.

171
00:17:47.390 --> 00:17:49.670
Think how that would make him feel!

172
00:17:52.240 --> 00:17:57.390
Carelessly showing the loser kindness
just adds insult to injury.

173
00:17:58.200 --> 00:18:02.810
He fought this duel knowing full well
it might turn out this way!

174
00:18:15.300 --> 00:18:16.900
It's hard...!

175
00:18:18.300 --> 00:18:20.450
That's called being a captain, isn't it?

176
00:18:21.400 --> 00:18:23.410
Don't doubt yourself.

177
00:18:26.010 --> 00:18:31.160
If you hesitate, who can we trust?

178
00:18:43.190 --> 00:18:45.020
We need to leave.

179
00:18:55.570 --> 00:19:01.610
We... can never come back
to this ship. Not ever again.
